duck: The Transitional Federal Government is the current internationally recognized government of the Republic of Somalia.

The Transitional Federal Government was the internationally recognized government of the Republic of Somalia until 20 August 2012, when its tenure officially ended and the Federal Government of Somalia was inaugurated.
